    <h2 class="new">ThinQ is an online experience similar to going to a cocktail party!
      </h2>
      <p>ThinQ.TV is a free platform where people can discover their passions. By participating in intellectual video chats, people can explore different opinons or enhance their skills through collaboration.
      </p>
